full_text:
Dear Ann,

Damn, you are a determined woman! ;-)

Very well. If you must know, yes I&#39;ve confronted darkness face to 
face. What some would call evil... calling my name. 

I was but a small child at the time, looking through crib slats. Long 
ago but never forgotten. Something I now know was a war for my soul 
took place, as much as that is odd to relate. Pleasing terror yawned 
wide, like sharp toothed jaws on one side, yet a light of infinite 
power and truth, a lighthouse within, finally sent her away, along 
with a simple decision I made, to embrace the highest and best.

That&#39;s about as much as I wish to say, since many will not understand 
let alone believe, until such a thing is revealed to them, as it was 
to me. It is so difficult to put such forces from within and beyond 
into words, and even harder to understand.   

LOL!

Suffice it to say I am a believer.

My quest in this life is to play a small part, a singular role, like 
a tiny ripple in the vast sea.

Nothing more. Nothing less.  

Lance

